[section#binary.search
    [`binary_search]
]

[%@library binary_search]
[codeblock:declaration]
template<class ForwardIterator, class T>
  constexpr bool
    binary_search(ForwardIterator first, ForwardIterator last,
                  const T& value);

template<class ForwardIterator, class T, class Compare>
  constexpr bool
    binary_search(ForwardIterator first, ForwardIterator last,
                  const T& value, Compare comp);
[codeblock:end]

[enter:description]
[para:requires]
[:en] The elements [`e] of [=range(first,last)] shall be partitioned with
respect to the expressions [`e < value] and [`!(value < e)] or [`comp(e, value)]
and [`!comp(value, e)].
[:zh_CN] [=range(first,last)] 中的元素 [`e] 应当根据表达式 [`e < value] 和
[`!(value < e)]，或者 [`comp(e, value)] 和 [`!comp(value, e)] 已分区。

[:en] Also, for all elements [`e] of [``[first, last)], [`e < value] shall imply
[`!(value < e)] or [`comp(e, value)] shall imply [`!comp(value, e)].
[:zh_CN] 并且，对于 [``[first, last)] 中的所有元素 [`e]，[`e < value] 应当蕴含
[`!(value < e)]，或者 [`comp(e, value)] 应当蕴含 [`!comp(value, e)]。

[para:returns]
[:en] [`true] if there is an iterator [`i] in the range [=range(first,last)]
that satisfies the corresponding conditions: [`!(*i < value) && !(value < *i)]
or [`comp(*i, value) == false && comp(value, *i) == false].
[:zh_CN] 如果 [=range(first,last)] 中存在符合以下对应条件的迭代器 [`i] 则返回
[`true]：[`!(*i < value) && !(value < *i)]
或者 [`comp(*i, value) == false && comp(value, *i) == false]。

[para:complexity]
[:en] At most [$\log_2([`last - first]) + [=O](1)] comparisons.
[:zh_CN] 最多 [$\log_2([`last - first]) + [=O](1)] 次比较。
[exit:description]
